L-R: Executive Director, Sales and Marketing, Skyway Aviation Handling Company PLC (SAHCO), Olaniyi Adigun ; Managing Director/CEO, SAHCO, Basil Agboarumi; Executive Director, Cargo Services and Operations, SAHCO, Boma Ukwunna cutting the cake at the Management Retreat. The retreat which is a culture of the SAHCO Management team to withdraw at the beginning of the year with the sole purpose to strategize, plan for the year and to also proffer solutions to challenges that are faced by the organization, ensured that all the Executive and Middle Level Managers from all the SAHCO stations in Nigeriawere in attendance.        